			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				    Trumpy can be found in the Fishes Ale in South Qeynos near the docks. THe best way to kill him is to follow him to the docks where he will pick on a fisherman that hangs out there. Wait till he gets all the way out there and then root him and kill him quickly, or else once the root wears off he will run to the other end of the docks and all his friends will come out and kill you quickly.<BR>
<BR>
    Now that you have his head, take it to kaladim and find byzar in the warrior guild. You MUST have at least amiable faction with him or else he'll just take the head from you. To get faction with stormguard, kill orcs at the orc pillar in BB. loc 0, -1200. Or kill krag chicks and also I have heard killing various goblins will give you faction with stormguard as well.
				</font>
